<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset='utf-8' />
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
			.header {
				background-color: #4f46e5;
				color: white;
				padding: 20px;
				text-align: center;
				border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
			}
			.content {
				padding: 20px;
				border: 1px solid #ddd;
				border-top: none;
				border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
			}
			.attendee-details {
				background-color: #f9f9f9;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
				border-radius: 5px;
				padding: 15px;
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.button {
				display: inline-block;
				background-color: #4f46e5;
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				padding: 10px 20px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				margin-top: 20px;
			}
			.footer {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #666;
				margin-top: 30px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class='header'>
			<h1>New Event Attendee!</h1>
		</div>

		<div class='content'>
			<p>Hello {{organizerName}},</p>

			<p>Good news! A new attendee has registered for your event
				<strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>.</p>

			<div class='attendee-details'>
				<h3>Attendee Information:</h3>
				<p><strong>Name:</strong> {{attendeeName}}</p>
				<p><strong>Email:</strong> {{attendeeEmail}}</p>
				<p><strong>Event:</strong> {{eventTitle}}</p>
				<p><strong>Event Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</p>
			</div>

			<p>You can check all registered attendees through your event management
				page:</p>

			<div style='text-align: center;'>
				<a href='{{eventUrl}}' class='button'>View Event Details</a>
			</div>

			<p>Thank you for using our platform to manage your events!</p>

			<p>Best regards,<br />UEvent Team</p>
		</div>

		<div class='footer'>
			<p>This is an automated message from UEvent.</p>
			<p>UEvent &copy; 2023. All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>